snippet.title: 1 vs. 100 - Nintendo DS
snippet.description:
This is a complete playthrough of 1 vs. 100 for the DS.
Review and scores in description.

Pros 
 +  Graphics well presented
 +  Decent Audio

Cons
 -  Limited replayability
 -  Needed some actual rewards for your winnings. Unlockables
